# where fields:
# - inst-sys	installation
# - default	default selection
# - slcs	SLCS
# - vpnncp	VPN/NCP
# - email	E-mail server
# - firewall	Firewall CD
# - expert_user Expert configuration - not available e.g. in personal edition
# - internal	internal package
#
# package		where			when
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

